description: Returns a list of publishing destinations associated with the specified detectorId.

parameters.name: DetectorId
parameters.description: The detector ID for which you want to retrieve the publishing destination. To find the detectorId in the current Region, see the Settings page in the GuardDuty console, or run the ListDetectors API.

nested_items.name: Destinations
nested_items.description: A Destinations object that includes information about each publishing destination returned.

nested_items.name: DestinationId
nested_items.description: The unique ID of the publishing destination.

nested_items.name: DestinationType
nested_items.description: The type of resource used for the publishing destination. Currently, only Amazon S3 buckets are supported.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The status of the publishing destination.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: A token to use for paginating results that are returned in the response. Set the value of this parameter to null for the first request to a list action. For subsequent calls, use the NextToken value returned from the previous request to continue listing results after the first page.
